SSH-KEYGEN
  # ssh-keygen -t dsa -f /root/key                -------------> -f= Specify key file location & its folder_name
  
Convert SSH keys to Different Format
  # ssh-keygen -e
        OR
  # ssh-keygen -e -f /root/.ssh/id_rsa > /root/.ssh/id_rsa.ssh2
  
    Enter file in which the key is (/root/.ssh/id_rsa):
